        <abstract> 
<p>Answers queries concerning errata in <hi rend="italic">Coral reefs</hi>.</p>  
<p>All copies of <hi rend="italic">Volcanic islands</hi> are sold. Smith, Elder &amp; Co. want to bring out a new edition, but CD is resolved not to look at a single proof.</p> 
